  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You have started to develop Deception beyond other skills, delving deeper into its possibilities.</p><p><strong>Core Feats</strong></p><ul><li>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.feats-srd.Item.Dvz54d6aPhjsmUux]{Lie to Me}</li></ul><p>Choose one Skill Path and gain that path's Trained feat.</p><p><strong>Available Skill Paths</strong></p><ul><li><strong>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e-skillpaths.pf2e-skillpath-compendium.Item.CiAxlrBn5hUVRQl2]{Intrigue Path - Trained}</strong>: You understand to use spoken words to weave intrigues and conspiracies.</li><li><strong>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e-skillpaths.pf2e-skillpath-compendium.Item.hcpYdOcHkp3Cgogk]{Identity Path - Trained}</strong>: You are a master of disguise, easily able to Impersonate whomever you want..</li><li><strong>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e-skillpaths.pf2e-skillpath-compendium.Item.YVHj8up9uSvgiY6o]{False Impressions Path - Trained}</strong>: You became a deceptively well lier, easily concealing the truth from anyone who shouldn't know it.</li></ul>",
